Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:08.81,Danna ga Nani Main,Hajime,0,0,0,,Você gostou dele?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.81,0:02:09.97,Danna ga Nani Main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sim.
